item.itunes:author: Eric Guidice
item.description:
Welcome to Yeats Music, where we bring you some of the great beats from the world of electronic music. Monthly podcasts display tracks which I have picked out of my record/MP3 crate to share with you. I tend to lean towards House Music (Electro, Funky, Progressive) but will always look outside the box when a good track comes by. On occasion we will have guest mixes, so look out for those. Check out track listings at yeatsmusic.com or myspace/yeatsmusic. Hope you enjoy and thanks for the continued support! Please feel free to leave feedback. Cheers!!
Eric Yeats Music

item.title: Yeats Music Vol.001
item.itunes:author: Eric Guidice
item.description:
Welcome to the first Yeats Music Podcast. 2008 is going to be a good year for electronic music. This month we bring you some Electro House and Trance. Tracklistings and a new website will be up and running in February; just in time for Yeats Music Podcast Vol. 002!!! Hope you enjoy. Let us know what you think and what you want to hear. Email us at: feedback@yeatsmusic.com
Cheers!!
- YeatsMusic.com
